s palm-sized, durably constructed in stainless steel, effective[^Yes, it really works!^], and blissfully ergonomic.%0a%0a'''Q E D'''&nbsp; You need one.%0a%0a[^#^]%0a%0a%0a[-A tip of the manifold to the [[http://www.kleinbottle.com | Acme Klein Bottle]] company.&nbsp; Add a [[http://www.kleinbottle.com/drinking_mug_klein_bottle.htm | Klein Stein]] to complete your nonorientable drinking experience!-]%0a(:linkwikiwords:)%0a
